quran[23{c,v,t}:
56,77,Innahoo la quraanun kareem
56,78,Fee kitaabim maknoon
56,79,Laa yamassuhooo illal mutahharoon
56,80,Tanzeelum mir Rabbil'aalameen
56,81,Afabihaazal hadeesi antum mudhinoon
56,82,Wa taj'aloona rizqakum annakum tukazziboon
56,83,Falaw laaa izaa balaghatil hulqoom
56,84,Wa antum heena'izin tanzuroon
56,85,Wa nahnu aqrabu ilaihi minkum wa laakil laa tubsiroon
56,86,Falaw laaa in kuntum ghira madeeneen
56,87,Tarji'oonahaaa in kuntum saadiqeen
56,88,Fa ammaaa in kaana minal muqarrabeen
56,89,Farawhunw wa raihaa nunw wa jannatu na'eem
56,90,Wa ammaaa in kaana min as haabil yameen
56,91,Fasalaamul laka min as haabil yameen
56,92,Wa ammaaa in kaana minal mukazzibeenad daaalleen
56,93,Fanuzulum min hameem
56,94,Wa tasliyatu jaheem
56,95,Inna haaza lahuwa haqqul yaqeen
56,96,Fasabbih bismi rabbikal 'azeem
57,1,Sabbaha lillaahi maa fissamaawaati wal ardi wa Huwal 'Azeezul Hakeem
57,2,Lahoo mulkus samaawaati wal ardi yuhyee wa yumeetu wa Huwa 'alaa kulli shai'in Qadeer
57,3,Huwal Awwalu wal'Aakhiru waz Zaahiru wal Baatinu wa huwa bikulli shai'in Aleem
